        <section name="X-ray Crystallography Refinement">
            <p>Algorithms to optimize an atomic resolution crystal structure against X-ray diffraction data.</p>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Command</th>
                        <th>Purpose</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <a href="commands/xray.Anneal.html">xray.Anneal</a>
                        </td>
                        <td>Run simulated annealing to optimize a structure using a reciprocal space objective
                            function.
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <a href="commands/xray.AverageMTZ.html">xray.AverageMTZ</a>
                        </td>
                        <td>Average multiple MTZ files.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <a href="commands/xray.CIF2MTZ.html">xray.CIF2MTZ</a>
                        </td>
                        <td>Convert a CIF diffraction file to MTZ format.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <a href="commands/xray.ComputeFc.html">xray.ComputeFc</a>
                        </td>
                        <td>Write out computed structure factors.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <a href="commands/xray.Deuterate.html">xray.Deuterate</a>
                        </td>
                        <td>Deuterate exchangable hydrogens of the PDB model.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <a href="commands/xray.Dynamics.html">xray.Dynamics</a>
